package:
  name: gcc_impl_linux-64
  version: 7.5.0
source:
  path: /home/conda/recipe_root
build:
  binary_relocation:
    - bin/*
    - lib/*.so*
    - libexec/**/*.so*
    - libexec/**/cc1*
    - libexec/**/collect2
    - libexec/**/gcc
    - libexec/**/lto*
    - libexec/**/plugin/gengtype
  detect_binary_files_with_prefix: false
  ignore_run_exports:
    - __glibc
  missing_dso_whitelist:
    - '*'
  number: 20
  runpath_whitelist:
    - x86_64-conda-linux-gnu/sysroot/lib/libpthread-2.12.2.so
  string: habd7529_20
requirements:
  host:
    - kernel-headers_linux-64 2.6.32 he073ed8_15
    - libgcc-ng 7.5.0 h2828fa1_20
    - libgfortran4 >=7.5.0,<8.0a0
    - libgomp 7.5.0 h2828fa1_20
    - libstdcxx-ng 7.5.0 h6de172a_20
    - sysroot_linux-64 2.12 he073ed8_15
  run:
    - binutils_impl_linux-64 >=2.31.1
    - libgcc-devel_linux-64 7.5.0 hda03d7c_20
    - libgcc-ng >=4.9
    - libgcc-ng >=7.5.0
    - libgomp >=7.5.0
    - libstdcxx-ng >=4.9
    - libstdcxx-ng >=7.5.0
    - sysroot_linux-64
test:
  commands:
    - echo x86_64-centos6-linux-gnu
    - echo 2.12.2
    - echo conda_cos6
    - echo 2.6.32
    - test -f ${PREFIX}/x86_64-conda-linux-gnu/sysroot/lib/libgomp.so
    - test `readlink ${PREFIX}/x86_64-conda-linux-gnu/sysroot/lib/libgomp.so` == "../../../lib/libgomp.so"
    - test -f ${PREFIX}/bin/x86_64-conda_cos6-linux-gnu-gcc
    - CC=$(${PREFIX}/bin/*-gcc -dumpmachine)-gcc
    - ${CC} -Wall tests/aligned_alloc.c -c -o c_aligned.o -v
    - ${CC} -Wall c_aligned.o -o c_aligned -v && ./c_aligned
  files:
    - tests
  requires:
    - sysroot_linux-64 2.12.*

  summary: GNU C Compiler
